The most stunning, vibrant tree I have ever seen is in a parking lot?! ❤️🍁 I styled this sporty, cropped, fuzzy jacket with sneakers but it goes equally well with booties ☺️ (Also for those asking, my hair is maintained by @lamiecramer 💕) Details for this look on the @liketoknow.it app or click the link in my profile 😘 http://liketk.it/2yjVD #liketkit
